{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9bf2ae1d20","title":"与陈昌奉同志的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"323443f49d","index":0,"year":1958,"month":8,"day":9,"articleId":"9bf2ae1d20","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"对话","id":"314ad57c4d","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui4","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1958-1960卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui4a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui4":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e24e1b9cf3","type":"title","text":"与陈昌奉同志的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"9bf2ae1d20","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ca09430515","type":"paragraph","text":"山东地方很好，根据地很大，新解放了许多县城，很需要干部。到那里要尊重地方，尊重地方干部，尊重新单位的负责人，要和当地干部搞好团结。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"9bf2ae1d20","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b9b37cba0f","type":"paragraph","text":"学习也好，倒不是为当官，而是为人民多做些事。当然，学习中间也有很多困难，只要你有为人民服务的决心，什么困难都能克服。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"9bf2ae1d20","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"eedcfa9f75","type":"paragraph","text":"指导员也是革命工作嘛!非当上什么官才行吗？","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"9bf2ae1d20","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"39ad27baf7","type":"paragraph","text":"想当官的人到共产党这里来就是走错门啦!我们这里还有什么官不官啊!都是一样。我们是为人民服务的，到我们这里发财当然不用说了。想升官也达不到目的．","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"9bf2ae1d20","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":657,"end":656}}}},"__N_SSG":true}